        <p>
          All calculators, tools, and estimates on ToolzTotal are provided for informational and educational purposes only. They do not constitute formal financial, real estate, investment, legal, medical, or tax advice. 
        </p>
        <blockquote>
          <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> While we endeavor to keep the mathematical formulas and rates up-to-date and accurate, we make no representations or warranties of any kind (express or implied) about the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of the results. You should consult a qualified professional before making any financial or legal decisions.
        </blockquote>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mt-8">3. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          In no event shall ToolzTotal, its contributors, or creators be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages arising out of your access to or use of the calculators. You assume full responsibility for any actions taken based on calculated outputs.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mt-8">4. Modifications to the Site</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any tools or aspects of the Site at any time without notice. All tools are offered for free without guarantees of uptime or permanent availability.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-ink mt-8">5. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms and conditions shall be governed by and construed in accordance with standard internet regulations. Any disputes arising under these terms shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the local courts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
